    <item>
      <title>意大利政府受挫 梅洛尼失去首位内阁成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/meloni-loses-culture-minister-in-new-challenge-to-her-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利文化部长在其部门中扮演的角色受到质疑后辞职，这是总理乔治亚·梅洛尼上任近两年来首次内阁辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/meloni-loses-culture-minister-in-new-challenge-to-her-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:43:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安哥拉将于十月出售最大保险公司的股份并上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/angola-to-sell-shares-in-biggest-insurer-list-firm-in-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉将出售其最大保险公司的股份，因为这个南部非洲国家正在加快其资产出售计划以增强其财政实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/angola-to-sell-shares-in-biggest-insurer-list-firm-in-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:24:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>敦促尼日利亚取消对抗议者可能判处的死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nigeria-urged-to-drop-possible-death-sentence-against-protesters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人权观察组织敦促尼日利亚撤销对上个月反政府示威活动中拘留的抗议者的叛国罪指控，该指控可能被判处死刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nigeria-urged-to-drop-possible-death-sentence-against-protesters</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:06:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国提议阻止中国在非洲建立军事基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-pitches-deal-to-thwart-chinese-military-base-in-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国正在为加蓬制定一项经济和安全援助计划，以阻止中国在这个具有战略地位的中非国家建立军事足迹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-pitches-deal-to-thwart-chinese-military-base-in-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:04:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
